{
  "stem": "18486.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when I got double ones for myself and my two, then, German daughters, I could use them to help the Jewish people who were hidden in our house.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know that I was German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, and I didn't give myself up to any group, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Leiden, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He occupied every--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every town or village and city was occupied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they confiscated places-- for instance, many Jewish houses, from Jews who had fled, were taken by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they had the [NON-ENGLISH], and, you know, and, you know, bridges.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saw them all the time, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hated those green uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Walking through our Dutch villages and see these.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it came in the papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We read about it, and, you know-- very shortly after the Germans had-- had occupied Holland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were-- there were German papers, certainly, in Holland, German newspapers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't want to read them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then they put it also in the Dutch papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we knew all about, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing secret about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't really remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That we all had to register ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, we were not allowed to have Jewish people in our house-- visiting, or living, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And things like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not every Jew looks Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't mean by-- I meant by clothing, or by--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, oh no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they had to wear the star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had that yellow, big star.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when that was an order, that we-- that all the Jewish people had to wear that star, we took stars, too, and wore them, to mix the Germans up.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
